name: gcc_impl_linux-ppc64le
raw_recipe:
# This file created by conda-build 3.20.3
# ------------------------------------------------

package:
    name: gcc_impl_linux-ppc64le
    version: 9.3.0
source:
    path: /home/conda/recipe_root
build:
    binary_relocation:
        - bin/*
        - lib/*.so*
        - libexec/**/*.so*
        - libexec/**/cc1*
        - libexec/**/collect2
        - libexec/**/gcc
        - libexec/**/lto*
        - libexec/**/plugin/gengtype
    detect_binary_files_with_prefix: false
    ignore_run_exports:
        - __glibc
        - libgcc-ng
    missing_dso_whitelist:
        - '*'
    number: 17
    runpath_whitelist:
        - x86_64-conda-linux-gnu/sysroot/lib/libpthread-2.12.2.so
    string: h60c02c0_17
requirements:
    host:
        - kernel-headers_linux-ppc64le 3.10.0 hbe0c576_10
        - sysroot_linux-ppc64le 2.17 h8b29623_10
    run:
        - binutils_impl_linux-ppc64le >=2.31.1
        - libgcc-devel_linux-ppc64le 9.3.0 h206f0cf_17
        - libgcc-ng >=4.9
        - libstdcxx-ng >=4.9
        - sysroot_linux-ppc64le
test:
    commands:
        - echo powerpc64le-unknown-linux-gnu
        - echo 2.17
        - echo conda_cos7
        - echo 3.10
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/powerpc64le-conda_cos7-linux-gnu-gcc
        - CC=$(${PREFIX}/bin/*-gcc -dumpmachine)-gcc
        - ${CC} -Wall tests/aligned_alloc.c -c -o c_aligned.o -v
    files:
        - tests
    requires:
        - sysroot_linux-ppc64le 2.17.*
about:
    home: https://gcc.gnu.org/
    license: GPL-3.0-only WITH GCC-exception-3.1
    summary: GNU C Compiler
extra:
    copy_test_source_files: true
    final: true
    recipe-maintainers:
        - beckermr
        - isuruf
